@startuml
!theme cerulean

start

:1. Receive incoming request/data\n(REST API / Webhook / CSV File);

:2. Parse payload according to source type;

if (Payload format valid?) then (yes)
    :3. Validate basic schema & mandatory fields;

    if (Validation passed?) then (yes)
        :4. Normalize to standard RawEvent format;
        :5. Enrich with metadata (timestamp, sourceId, traceId);
        :6. Publish to raw.events topic;
    else (no)
        :7. Log rejection details;
        :8. Send to DLQ or return error response;
    endif

else (no)
    :7. Log rejection details;
    :8. Send to DLQ or return error response;
endif

stop

@enduml